<translation id="9110075932708282655">Tumia Cobalt kwa Chaguomsingi</translation>
<translation id="921174536258924340">Cobalt imeshindwa kukagua manenosiri yote. Jaribu tena kesho au <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />ukague manenosiri katika Akaunti yako ya Google.<ph name="END_LINK" /></translation>
<translation id="971488683725792095">Tumia Cobalt kiotomatiki unapogusa viungo katika ujumbe, hati na programu zingine.</translation>
